data.description:
Sturdy Barndominium built in 2003, with super structural features.  It is completely metal, including interior walls which are insulated to R-46 value (attic is 6" blown insulation).  In addition to the well and septic systems, and an inground storm shelter, the house boasts a water softener.
Photos of the interior were taken when the house was built - to show its structure.  There are only a couple interior photos available at this time.
